data.description: Charming 1905 Tudor on historic Levens St in Dallas! This gem boasts updates like new flooring, tilt-in vinyl windows, and a modern HVAC system with AC. A 561sf addition offers a new bathroom and kitchenette, perfect for a rec room, office, or guest house. Enjoy a fully fenced backyard with 2 paver patios, raised garden beds, a garden shed, and a dog run. Plus, RV parking with hookup! Nestled in a tree-lined neighborhood, you're close to downtown and Dallas City Park. Welcome home!
